'''Aɣeṛda''' ([[Assaɣ ussnan]]: ''Mus'') d [[tawsit (tudersent)|tawsit]] n [[aɣersiw|iɣersiwen]] yeṭṭafaren [[tawacult (tasnudert)|tawacult]] n [[tiɣeṛdayin|tɣeṛdayin]] deg [[tafesna|tfesna]] n [[Timseɣẓaẓ|temseɣẓaẓ]], Talmest tamezdayt dges s waṭas d [[aɣeṛda n wexxam]]. <br/> 
Iɣeṛdayen s yakk [[talmest|tilmas-is]] ttmilen ad idiren deg yidgan yudsen (iqerben) ar ifganen 

Yettidir uɣeṛds 3 n iseggasen. Maca drus kan iy ttaweṭ ar [[addar|waddar-a]] acku yetteɣlay d [[tagemra|tagemrawt]] i [[Amcic|yimcac]] d [[aydi|iṭan]] d [[abareɣ|iburaɣ]] d [[azrem|izerman]] yakk d [[tiwukin|tiwukin]]

== Aglam ==
[[Tiddi (tusnakt)|Tiddi]] n uɣeṛda d tin yettilin gar n 12 ar 21 cm, [[Azuk|yettazen]] gar n 7 arc57 g, tafekka tafekka-ynes d tin yemgaraden gar n umellal d uras 

== [[Amyaraw]] ==
Iɣeṛdayen d [[aɣersiw|iɣersiwen]] ilan anagraw n [[Amyaraw|umyaraw]] amegzu yettbaddiden mgal n imihiyen id yettmagaren, yezmer ad yarew mi ara ad yaweṭ deg waddar-is 50 n wussan ama i [[Awtem|wewtem]] neɣ i [[Tawtemt|tewtemt]]
